testcase.name: AppComponent should create the app
HeaderComponent should be created
NavbarComponent should be created
NavbarComponent should define the store
NavbarComponent should define subsections
NavbarComponent should display subsection in template
NavbarComponent should call dispatchAction() when subsection is clicked
NavbarComponent should dispatch action when dispatchAction is called
NewsItemComponent should be created
NewsItemComponent should display title in template
NewsItemComponent should display news abstract in template
NewsComponent should create
NewsComponent should define the store
SectionsComponent should create the component
SectionsComponent should store the sections in array: sectionList
SectionsComponent should display the section name in DOM
NewsService should be created
NewsService should get results
The news reducer should load news, when LOAD_SECTION_NEWS dispatched
The news reducer should update the filter, when FILTER_SUBSECTION is dispatched
The news reducer should return the list of news, when getNewsList() is called
The news reducer should return the filter value, when getFilter() is called
The sections reducer should return the list of sections, when LOAD_SECTIONS is dispatched
The sections reducer should return the initial state if no action is dispatched
